text: Ishalino () is a rural locality (a village) in Rostovsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 223 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 21 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye, 10 km from Telyashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Ishalino
